OBJECTIVES: Installing/Configuring APACHE

- Required packages for Installing  
        -httpd
        -firewalld

- Run and enable services Required

- Vhost configuration

- port redirection

- load initial index page 



TIPS/LESSONS LEARNED:

adding 'serial: 1' to the playbook so that the webserver stays up and running 
while the other goes down.

Having an undo playbook makes life a bit more bearable. 

verify webpage playbook to quickly verify it's up and running and returning content

callback_whitelist = profile_tasks in ansible.cfg gives tasks time completion.